'''丽塔·亚历山德里·萨尔基相''' ({{lang-hy|Ռիտա Ալեքսանդրի Սարգսյան}}, ''née'' Dadayan ({{lang|hy|Դադայան}}), 1962年3月6日 - 2020年11月20日<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Մահացել է Ռիտա Սարգսյանը|url=https://armeniatoday.news/armenia/200645/|access-date=2020-11-20|website=Armenia Today|language=hy-AM|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203101251/https://armeniatoday.news/armenia/200645/|dead-url=no}}</ref>) ，2008至2018年期间为[[亚美尼亚第一夫人|亚美尼亚第一夫人]]，出生于一个军人家庭，生前职业为音乐教师<ref name="official bio">{{Cite web |url=http://www.president.am/en/first-lady/ |title=Official website of the President of Armenia. Rita Sargsyan. First Lady of Armenia |accessdate=2021-01-15 |archive-date=2016-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160504053308/http://www.president.am/en/first-lady/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://armenpress.am/arm/news/707797 |title=Documentary "Married to the president", «Rossia 24» (''in Armenian'') |accessdate=2021-01-15 |archive-date=2017-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201033221/https://armenpress.am/arm/news/707797 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
== 婚姻 ==
1983年，与[[谢尔日·萨尔基相|谢尔日·萨尔基相]]结婚。二人育有两个女儿Anush和Satenik，以及四个外孙Mariam、Rita、Ara以及Serzh。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://galatv.am/hy/news/105643/|title=«Հասարակությանը ներկայացնելու այնքան քիչ բան ունեն, որ Հռոմի Պապի տված պատարագն են սեփականացնում»|website=ԳԱԼԱ|language=hy-AM|accessdate=2016-03-03|archive-date=2018-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181220154504/http://galatv.am/hy/news/105643/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.a1plus.am/77146.html|title=Հարցը Զարուհուն հուշել էր Սերժ Սարգսյանը|website=www.a1plus.am|accessdate=2016-03-03|archive-date=2019-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190823163136/https://www.a1plus.am/77146.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.7or.am/am/news/view/43739/|title=Միշիկական քարոզչամեքենան «բուքսավատ» է անում|last=Intell-Sol.com|website=www.7or.am|accessdate=2016-03-03|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211094435/https://www.7or.am/am/news/view/43739/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==去世==
2020年11月20日，丽塔·萨尔基相因感染[[2019冠状病毒病|新冠病毒]]逝世，享年58岁。<ref name=":0" /> [[尼科尔·帕希尼扬|尼科尔·帕希尼扬]]总理发表唁电，表示“其在促进本国文化的社会和公共活动中发挥了引领作用”。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Prime Minister Nikol Pashinyan’s Condolence Message on Passing of Rita Sargsyan|url=https://www.primeminister.am/en/condolence/item/2020/11/20/Nikol-Pashinyan-Condolences/|access-date=2020-11-21|website=www.primeminister.am|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121045053/https://www.primeminister.am/en/condolence/item/2020/11/20/Nikol-Pashinyan-Condolences/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[阿尔缅·萨尔基相|阿尔缅·萨尔基相]]总统亲自慰问了[[谢尔日·萨尔基相|谢尔日]]并表达了他的哀思。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Armen Sarkissian expresses condolences to and visits Armenia 3rd President Serzh Sargsyan|url=https://news.am/eng/news/614928.html|access-date=2020-11-23|website=news.am|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121070815/https://news.am/eng/news/614928.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

